WITH weekly_by_type AS (
    SELECT 
        -- Snowflake weeks start Sunday by default
        DATE_TRUNC('week', DATE) as week_start,
        CAMPAIGN_TYPE,
        SUM(SPEND) as cost,
        SUM(IMPRESSIONS) as impressions,
        SUM(CLICKS) as clicks,
        SUM(SIGN_UPS) as sign_ups,
        SUM(PAYWALL) as paywall,
        SUM(CUSTOMERS) as customers,
        SUM(DEMOS_BOOKED) as demos_booked,
        SUM(DEMOS_COMPLETE) as demos_complete
    FROM TRAINING_DATABASE.PUBLIC.MART_GOOGLE_ADS_PERFORMANCE
    WHERE DATE >= DATEADD('day', -35, CURRENT_DATE)
    GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('week', DATE), CAMPAIGN_TYPE
),

-- Add calculated metrics per campaign type
with_metrics AS (
    SELECT 
        week_start,
        CAMPAIGN_TYPE,
        -- Volume metrics
        cost,
        impressions,
        clicks,
        sign_ups,
        paywall,
        customers,
        demos_booked,
        demos_complete,
        -- Cost metrics
        cost / NULLIF(clicks, 0) as cpc,
        cost / NULLIF(sign_ups, 0) as cpsu,
        cost / NULLIF(paywall, 0) as cppc,
        cost / NULLIF(customers, 0) as cac,
        cost / NULLIF(demos_booked, 0) as cpdb,
        cost / NULLIF(demos_complete, 0) as cpdc,
        -- Rate metrics (as decimals, multiply by 100 for %)
        clicks::FLOAT / NULLIF(impressions, 0) as ctr,
        sign_ups::FLOAT / NULLIF(clicks, 0) as sign_up_rate,
        paywall::FLOAT / NULLIF(sign_ups, 0) as paywall_rate,
        customers::FLOAT / NULLIF(paywall, 0) as customer_rate,
        -- Clicks per demo metrics
        clicks::FLOAT / NULLIF(demos_booked, 0) as clicks_pdb,
        clicks::FLOAT / NULLIF(demos_complete, 0) as clicks_pdc
    FROM weekly_by_type
),

-- Calculate weekly totals
weekly_totals AS (
    SELECT 
        week_start,
        'Total' as CAMPAIGN_TYPE,
        SUM(cost) as cost,
        SUM(impressions) as impressions,
        SUM(clicks) as clicks,
        SUM(sign_ups) as sign_ups,
        SUM(paywall) as paywall,
        SUM(customers) as customers,
        SUM(demos_booked) as demos_booked,
        SUM(demos_complete) as demos_complete,

        SUM(cost) / NULLIF(SUM(sign_ups), 0) as cpsu,
        SUM(cost) / NULLIF(SUM(paywall), 0) as cppc,
        SUM(cost) / NULLIF(SUM(customers), 0) as cac,
        SUM(cost) / NULLIF(SUM(demos_booked), 0) as cpdb,
        SUM(cost) / NULLIF(SUM(demos_complete), 0) as cpdc,

        SUM(paywall)::FLOAT / NULLIF(SUM(sign_ups), 0) as paywall_rate,

        -- Clicks per demo

        SUM(clicks)::FLOAT / NULLIF(SUM(demos_complete), 0) as clicks_pdc

-- Email Type Weekly Trend (Qualified vs Unqualified, All Campaigns)
WITH weekly AS (
    SELECT 
        DATE_TRUNC('week', DATE)::DATE as week_start,
        SUM(SPEND) as spend,
        SUM(CLICKS) as clicks,
        SUM(SIGN_UPS) as all_sign_ups,
        SUM(QUALIFIED_SIGN_UPS) as qualified_sign_ups,
        SUM(PAYWALL) as all_paywall,
        SUM(QUALIFIED_TRIALS) as qualified_paywall,
        SUM(CUSTOMERS) as all_customers,
        SUM(QUALIFIED_FIRST_PAYMENT) as qualified_customers
    FROM TRAINING_DATABASE.PUBLIC.MART_GOOGLE_ADS_PERFORMANCE
    WHERE DATE >= DATEADD('day', -21, CURRENT_DATE)
    GROUP BY 1
),

unpivoted AS (
    -- Qualified (Work Email)
    SELECT 
        week_start,
        'Qualified' as email_type,
        spend,
        clicks,
        qualified_sign_ups as sign_ups,
        qualified_paywall as paywall,
        qualified_customers as customers
    FROM weekly
    
    UNION ALL
    
    -- Unqualified (Personal Email)
    SELECT 
        week_start,
        'Unqualified' as email_type,
        spend,
        clicks,
        all_sign_ups - qualified_sign_ups as sign_ups,
        all_paywall - qualified_paywall as paywall,
        all_customers - qualified_customers as customers
    FROM weekly
)

SELECT 
    week_start,
    email_type,
    
    -- 1. Sign Ups
    sign_ups,
    
    -- 2. Sign Up Rate (%)
    ROUND(sign_ups::FLOAT / NULLIF(clicks, 0) * 100, 2) as sign_up_rate_pct,
    
    -- 3. Cost Per Sign Up
    ROUND(spend / NULLIF(sign_ups, 0), 2) as cpsu,
    
    -- 4. Paywall Complete
    paywall,
    
    -- 5. Paywall Complete Rate (%)
    ROUND(ROUND(paywall)::FLOAT / NULLIF(sign_ups, 0) * 100, 2) as paywall_rate_pct,
    
    -- 6. Cost Per Paywall Complete
    ROUND(spend / NULLIF(paywall, 0), 2) as cppc,
    
    -- 7. Customers
    customers,
    
    -- 8. Customer Rate (%)
    ROUND(customers::FLOAT / NULLIF(paywall, 0) * 100, 2) as customer_rate_pct,
    
    -- 9. CAC
    ROUND(spend / NULLIF(customers, 0), 2) as cac

FROM unpivoted
WHERE sign_ups >= 0 AND paywall >= 0 AND customers >= 0
ORDER BY week_start, email_type
